{"word":"G4411 - πρωτοκλισία - prōtoklisía - pro-tok-lis-ee'-ah - Chief","slug":"G4411","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">πρωτοκλισία</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>prōtoklisía"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>pro-tok-lis-ee'-ah"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Chief"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C0;&#x03C1;&#x03C9;&#x03C4;&#x03BF;&#x03BA;&#x03BB;&#x03B9;&#x03C3;&#x03B9;&#x0301;&#x03B1; - pro&#x0304;toklisia</b> - <i>pro-tok-lis-ee'-ah</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G4413\">G4413</a> and <a href=\"#/G2828\">G2828</a>; a <i>reclining first</i> (in the place of honor) at the dinner bed, that is, <i>preeminence</i> at meals: - chief (highest, uppermost) room."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G4409\">G4409</a>, <a href=\"#/G4410\">G4410</a>, <a href=\"#/G4412\">G4412</a>, <a href=\"#/G4413\">G4413</a>, <a href=\"#/G4414\">G4414</a>, <a href=\"#/G4415\">G4415</a>, <a href=\"#/G4416\">G4416</a>"}]}